[4
Date: 23 Aug 2001
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: Financial Times World Media Abstract Service: European, 22 Aug 2001

Suspected case of BSE in Brescia
--------------------------------
Initial tests carried out on a cow from a farm near the northern Italian
town of Brescia have proved positive for BSE. Further tests to confirm the
results will now be carried out on the animal. To date, 26 confirmed cases
of BSE have been discovered in Italy.
